nosis of the disease</a></li> <li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#лечение">Treatment</a></li> <li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#возможные-осложнения">Possible complications</a></li> <li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#профилактика">Prophylaxis</a></li> <li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#прогноз">Forecast</a></li> <li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#какие-вопросы-нужно-задать-врачу">What questions should you ask your doctor?</a></li> <li class="toc-entry toc-h2"><a href="#список-использованной-литературы">•  List of used literature</a></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="waved-container-wrapper"> <div class="waved-container"> <div class="green-wave"></div> <div class="light-wave"></div> <div class="waved-container-content"> <div class="wrapper"> <h3>Other diseases in this section</h3> <ul class="related-list"> <li class="related-item"> <a class="related-item__link" href="gipoparatireoz.html"> <h5 class="related-item__title">Hypoparathyroidism</h5> <p class="related-item__text">A disease in which too little parathyroid hormone is synthesized in the body, which leads to a lack of calcium.</p> </a> </li> <li class="related-item"> <a class="related-item__link" href="sakharnyy-diabet-2-tipa.html"> <h5 class="related-item__title">Type 1 diabetes</h5> <p class="related-item__text">A disease in which high blood sugar (glucose) is due to the body losing its ability to respond to insulin.</p> </a> </li> <li class="related-item"> <a class="related-item__link" href="diffuznyi-toksicheskii-zob.html"> <h5 class="related-item__title">Diffuse toxic goiter</h5> <p class="related-item__text">An autoimmune thyroid disease characterized by excessive production of thyroid hormones (T3 and T4).</p> </a> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <hzy-kb-menu-toggle></hzy-kb-menu-toggle>

        



